Global EMI Shielding Laminates Market Insights
EMI Shielding Laminates Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.4% from 2024 to 2030.

EMI Shielding Laminates Market Overview
The global EMI Shielding Laminates market size is expected to grow significantly, reaching a market value of USD 5.7 billion by 2027, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.1% from 2020. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for electronic devices, especially in the automotive and consumer electronics sectors, where EMI shielding is essential to protect sensitive components from electromagnetic interference. Moreover, technological advancements and stricter regulations regarding electromagnetic pollution in several industries are contributing to the market’s expansion. As industries like telecommunications, healthcare, and automotive continue to embrace new technologies, the need for efficient EMI shielding solutions will increase, thus supporting the market growth.

